dc_title_s: A Map to illustrate Captain Harcourt's paper on the Himalayan valleys of Kooloo, Lahoul & Spiti, with a sketch map of the passes from India to Eastern Turkistan
dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures, spot heights, and shading. Major passes and glaciers are shown. Primary map shows boundaries between major valleys. Sketch map shows boundary of British territory. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 41 (1871), pp.245-57; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687
dc_creator_sm: Harcourt, A. F. P. (Alfred Frederick Pollock), 1836-1910
dc_publisher_s: London : published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society, by J. Murray, Albemarle Street, 1871.
